itemLabel: Derek Moore-Brabazon, 2nd Baron Brabazon of Tara

wikipedia_page.main: Derek Charles Moore-Brabazon, 2nd Baron Brabazon of Tara  (24 December 1910 – 11 December 1974), succeeded the title Baron Brabazon of Tara in 1964 on the death of his father, John Cuthbert Moore-Brabazon, 1st Baron Brabazon of Tara, carrying it for just ten years until his death in 1974.
